bbc449f0-1c22-5554-a66d-dc97256a30e4,tg:rubgr:394,e73_Descriptions,,id.desc,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"BRUEGEL, Rebel Angels cf. BECCAFUMI (fire pictures!) see Donato SANMINIATELLI, Domenico Beccafumi, Milano [Bramante], 1967, Night with fire: Aeneas saving Anchises, Fresco in Pal. Bindi Sergardi, Siena, pl. 315 either 1524-25 Sanminiatelli) or 1528-30 (others). St. Michael & the Rebel Angels, Siena, Pinacoteca intended for church of Carmine, c. 1524-25, pl. 36 unfinished (few monsters, mainly male nudes) with darkness & fire. St. Michael & Rebel Angels, Siena Chiesa del Carmine, pl. 43, (colour plate of detail facing p. 96). Different composition, final version; variously dated: c. 1538, or c. 1525-26. Here God Father surrounded by angels at top. One monster only at bottom.",descriptive note,Nederlands,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,

column4: <content>BRUEGEL, Rebel Angels cf. BECCAFUMI (fire pictures!) see Donato SANMINIATELLI, Domenico Beccafumi, Milano [Bramante], 1967, Night with fire: Aeneas saving Anchises, Fresco in Pal. Bindi Sergardi, Siena, pl. 315 either 1524-25 Sanminiatelli) or 1528-30 (others). St. Michael & the Rebel Angels, Siena, Pinacoteca intended for church of Carmine, c. 1524-25, pl. 36 unfinished (few monsters, mainly male nudes) with darkness & fire. St. Michael & Rebel Angels, Siena Chiesa del Carmine, pl. 43, (colour plate of detail facing p. 96). Different composition, final version; variously dated: c. 1538, or c. 1525-26. Here God Father surrounded by angels at top. One monster only at bottom.</content>
